{"tid":1276960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發完一場美夢，咁下一步點？","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:24:21.000Z","uid":121048,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5dcb5ef86dc4de4159344ec172d6dc20646baf","tid":1276960,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"琴晚成功攻佔立法會，可以話係一個大突破，成功突破咗好多人香港人嘅心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信經歷立法會一役，下一次我地會變得更有勇氣將行動升級，將會少咗好多心理包袱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地未贏架！</span><br />\n<br />\n七一，我地有天時之利。不過接下來，我地都未必有呢啲契機，所以我覺得我地好有必要諗定下一步嘅方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會唔會繼續落區宣傳？會唔會再訂立下一個deadline ?仲有好多野要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好掉以輕心啊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要記得，我地從來都冇贏過！</span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好一直沉醉係美夢當中啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然我都好唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7ba2c754dda0afad8601444abe80f03b0e67b225","tid":1276960,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:36:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c03347e19b7f3d61d5e030e437e0b33ef85125f","tid":1276960,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"746a9965f06ff0eb02aaa7139e98653bb0705022","tid":1276960,"uid":36088,"like":0,"